      "note": "This moral truth is among those to which the first sentence of verse 15 of this surah alludes, and its succinct formulation fully explains the reason why the story of Cain and Abel is mentioned in this context. The expression \"We have ordained unto the children of Israel\" does not, of course, detract from the universal validity of this moral: it refers merely to its earliest enunciation."
