      "note": "The present participle la-musrifun indicates their \"continuously committing excesses\" (i.e., crimes), and is best rendered as \"they go on committing\" them. In view of the preceding passages, these \"excesses\" obviously refer to crimes of violence and, in particular, to the ruthless killing of human beings."
